{"id":"291437226_Regularization_and_the_small-ball_method_I_Sparse_recovery","abstract":"We obtain bounds on estimation error rates for regularization procedures of\nthe form \\begin{equation*}\n\\hat f \\in {\\rm argmin}_{f\\in\nF}\\left(\\frac{1}{N}\\sum_{i=1}^N\\left(Y_i-f(X_i)\\right)^2+\\lambda\n\\Psi(f)\\right) \\end{equation*} when $\\Psi$ is a norm and $F$ is convex.\nOur approach gives a common framework that may be used in the analysis of\nlearning problems and regularization problems alike. In particular, it sheds\nsome light on the role various notions of sparsity have in regularization and\non their connection with the size of subdifferentials of $\\Psi$ in a\nneighbourhood of the true minimizer.\nAs `proof of concept' we extend the known estimates for the LASSO, SLOPE and\ntrace norm regularization.","authors":["Guillaume Lecu√©","Shahar Mendelson"],"meta":["January 2016The Annals of Statistics 46(2)","DOI:10.1214/17-AOS1562","SourcearXiv"],"references":["266856478_Learning_without_Concentration_for_General_Loss_Functions","263967823_SLOPE_--_Adaptive_Variable_Selection_via_Convex_Optimization","236871757_Learning_subgaussian_classes_Upper_and_minimax_bounds","220320030_On_model_selection_consistency_of_LASSO","47843632_Nuclear_norm_penalization_and_optimal_rates_for_noisy_low_rank_matrixcompletion","47397135_A_Unified_Framework_for_High-Dimensional_Analysis_of_M-Estimators_with_Decomposable_Regularizers","23418923_p_-Values_for_High-Dimensional_Regression","2130019_High_dimensional_graphs_and_variable_selection_with_the_LASSO","1908927_Sup-norm_convergence_rate_and_sign_concentration_property_of_Lasso_and_Dantzig_estimators","1906147_Simultaneous_analysis_of_LASSO_and_Dantzig_selector","1896344_Guaranteed_Minimum-Rank_Solutions_of_Linear_Matrix_Equations_via_Nuclear_Norm_Minimization","1752232_Lasso-Type_Recovery_of_Sparse_Representations_for_High-Dimensional_Data","313775713_Sparse_recovery_under_weak_moment_assumptions","307307316_Regularization_and